    dc:title="One vote in four..."
    dc:identifier="http://www.notapathetic.com/comments/114"
    dc:description="One vote in four years is not democracy. The government talk about having the mandate of the people to go to war, even when the people were noisily against it. I'd like to remind Tony Blair that he and his party..."
    dc:creator="NotApathetic.com"
